OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fsome brighter intervals and the odd
OL,7,Fspot of rain possible. Remaining
OL,8,Fcloudy in the afternoon with outbreaks
OL,9,Fof mostly light rain spreading
OL,10,Feastwards. Some brighter spells
OL,11,Fpossible in the east. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be cloudy through the
OL,14,Fevening and overnight with outbreaks
OL,15,Fof light rain possible, mainly in the
OL,16,Fwest. The best of any drier spells in
OL,17,Fthe east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
