OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Foccasional outbreaks of light and
OL,7,Fpatchy rain. Rain mainly in the west
OL,8,Fwith the best of the drier and
OL,9,Fbrighter spells in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fwith outbreaks of rain at times on
OL,13,FTuesday. Wednesday will be dry with
OL,14,Fsunny spells, becoming warm in the
OL,15,Feast. Mostly dry Thursday with some
OL,16,Fbright or sunny intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
